# Docker Tips (works with colima)
# Format: alias|old_command_pattern|description|example

d|docker |Short alias for docker|d ps
dc|docker-compose|Short for docker-compose|dc up -d
dps|docker ps|List running containers|dps
di|docker images|List images|di
drm|docker rm|Remove container|drm container_name
drmi|docker rmi|Remove image|drmi image:tag
dstop|docker stop|Stop all running containers|dstop
drmall|docker rm|Remove all containers|drmall
colima-start|colima|Start colima (Docker runtime)|colima-start
colima-stop|colima|Stop colima|colima-stop
colima-status|colima|Check colima status|colima-status
